event OwnershipTransferred(address indexed previousOwner, address indexed newOwner)
event RecurringOrderUpdated(address sellToken, address buyToken, uint256 sellAmount, uint256 interval, uint256 startTimestamp)
function checkUpkeep(bytes) view returns (bool upkeepNeeded, bytes performData)
function getAllOrders(address _user) view returns (tuple(address sellToken, address buyToken, uint256 sellAmount, uint256 lastExecution, uint256 interval)[] orders)
function getOrderData(bytes32 _tokenPairHash, bytes32 _orderHash) view returns (tuple(address user, uint256 sellAmount, uint256 lastExecution, uint256 interval))
function swapExactTokensForTokens(address _tokenIn, address _tokenOut, uint256 _amountIn, address _user) returns (bool)
